WEBVTT

00:05:57.633 --> 00:06:01.550
because the activist investors have no
issues getting management to make changes.

00:06:01.574 --> 00:06:04.100
They have no issues turning up the heat.

00:06:04.124 --> 00:06:05.322
Take Paul Singer.

00:06:05.346 --> 00:06:07.689
He's an old-school Wall Street OG,

00:06:07.713 --> 00:06:11.421
now in his 70s, loves Doritos,
loves making money.

00:06:12.474 --> 00:06:15.881
Argentina owed Paul 600 million dollars

00:06:15.905 --> 00:06:17.816
and would not pay.

00:06:18.386 --> 00:06:19.552
Big mistake.

00:06:19.576 --> 00:06:22.987
You can't take money from an OG
and not pay it back.

00:06:23.425 --> 00:06:25.872
Paul went to war with Argentina.

00:06:25.896 --> 00:06:27.990
I am not inventing.

00:06:28.014 --> 00:06:29.583
This is big. This was huge.

00:06:29.607 --> 00:06:32.246
This was bigger than Tyson vs Holyfield,